LISTSERV Web Interface 2.4.1 2014-05-09T13:08:25Z JiscMail Helpline 2014-05-09T15:07:57+01:00 2014-05-09T15:07:57+01:00 BTG JiscMail List - is CLOSED https://www.jiscmail.ac.uk:443/cgi-bin/webadmin?A2=BTG;b0a624ac.1405 We have been unable to find a new list owner therefore JiscMail have CLOSED this list.<br><br>The list is not accepting new subscribers and existing subscribers are no longer able to post messages to the list. The list archives will continue to be available to browse.<br><br>We can reactivate this list if we can find a new list owner. To volunteer please contact us at helpline@jiscmail.ac.uk - we can provide training and support. [...] JiscMail Helpline 2014-04-16T16:47:12+01:00 2014-04-16T16:47:12+01:00 Reminder: Message regarding BTG JiscMail List https://www.jiscmail.ac.uk:443/cgi-bin/webadmin?A2=BTG;aa32bc92.1404 We urgently require an existing subscriber(s) of this list to take over the running of the list.<br><br>The previous list owners cannot be contacted and so JiscMail are temporarily running this list until a new owner can be found.<br><br>If you would like to volunteer to help keep this list open and active, please contact us at helpline@jiscmail.ac.uk - we can provide training and support if needed.
